She walked over to Scorponok and put her hand on his shoulder.  She leaned 
over to see the computer screen.  She reached down and pointed to a blip on 
the screen. "Is that Quickstrike? And that other blip right next to him 
is..who? and that one in the trees is an old friend of his? Cheetor?  I've 
never met him.  Is he one of us?"
She looked to make sure that Megatron wasn't looking and stole a kiss from 
Scorponok. She smiled and walked over to her console.
